Classes/RESolution.html#/s:18LeetCode_So.name: removeElement(_:_:)
Classes/RESolution.html#/s:18LeetCode_So.abstract: Given an integer array nums and an integer val, remove all occurrences of val in nums in-place.

Classes/RDSolution.html#/s:18LeetCode_So.name: removeDuplicates(_:)
Classes/RDSolution.html#/s:18LeetCode_So.abstract: Given an integer array nums sorted in non-decreasing order, remove the duplicates in-place such that each unique element appears only once. The relative order of the elements should be kept the same. Then return the number of unique elements in nums.
